Beneficial effects of indigenous Bacillus spp. on growth, antioxidants, immunity 
and disease resistance of Rhynchocypris lagowskii.

Elsadek MM(1), Zhu W(2), Wang S(2), Wang X(2), Guo Z(3), Lin L(4), Wang G(2), 
Wang Q(2), Chen Y(5), Zhang D(6).

Author information:
(1)College of Animal Science and Technology, Key Laboratory for Animal 
Production Quality and Safety of Ministry of Education, Jilin Provincial Key 
Laboratory of Animal Nutrition and Feed Science, Jilin Agricultural University, 
Changchun, 130118, China; Department of Fish Production, Faculty of Agriculture, 
Al-Azhar University, Cairo, 11884, Egypt.
(2)College of Animal Science and Technology, Key Laboratory for Animal 
