Evaluation of bone mineral density, microarchitecture, and detection of 
fractures on young patients living with human immunodeficiency virus: when and 
how to screen?

Gehrke B(1)(2)(3), Farias MLF(4), Wildemberg LE(5), Ferraiuoli GI(6), Ribeiro 
V(6), Bosgnoli R(7), Paranhos Neto FP(4), de Mendonça LMC(8), Madeira M(4), 
